        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend title XVIII of the Social Security Act to modernize and improve the Medicare payment methodology for radiopharmaceuticals under the hospital outpatient prospective payment system and to ensure equitable payment and patient access to certain low volume, high cost radiopharmaceuticals.</title>
